Legendary Pink Dots.about:
This is an exclusive teaser created from the epic 19 minute journey entitled "The Man Who Floated Away" by Steven Stapleton and Edward Ka-Spel. Essentially an album representing old friendships the piece is complemented by a side-long work by Colin Potter and Quentin Rollet on the other side of this vinyl release from Bisou Records. The stunning artwork is by Steven Stapleton. 

Please note that this release is ALSO available via Bisou Records at:  bisou-records.com  and Integrated Circuit Records at:  icrdistribution.com



